"PBS Encore" isn't really an official name for anything; it seems to be what RabbitEars uses for largely-station-programmed (as opposed to a network-unto-itself such as Create, World, and the PBS Kids Channel), usually-non-primary-channel lineups of mainly-PBS programming, to distinguish those channels from the "regular" PBS feed. I don't think there's any correlation with any PBS national schedules.
